        <mxCell id="528OkdiDyzRQrP8GUQJY-48" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="&lt;b&gt;To Design a Youtube Like Video Streaming Platform&lt;/b&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;1. Functional Requirements&lt;/b&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Users can upload videos.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Users can watch videos.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Users can search about videos.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Users can like/unlike videos and post comments with real-time count updates.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;The system supports search, recommendations, and channel subscriptions.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Users can sign up, log in, and manage their channels and uploaded content.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;2. Non-Functional Requirements&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;Availability &amp;gt; Consistency&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;The system must scale to handle millions of concurrent viewers and uploads.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Video playback should start quickly and switch quality without noticeable buffering. Even at low bandwidth.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;The platform must maintain high availability (99.9% uptime or higher).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Likes and comments should update dynamically with low latency.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;3. Core Entities&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;User&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Channel&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Video&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Like and Comments&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Recommendation Feed&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="390" width="490" x="-1020" y="-800" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
